even though I don't necessarily agree with your statement I respect it. 
Terraform / opentofu and terragrunt are de facto tools for IaC and tenv actually aims to bring together the functionality of 3 relevant tools around this ecosystem.  therefore stargazers might not actually represent how relevant the tool is. 

